trans-unit.source: Represents a design-time editor sheet for the properties of a <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""></xref> expression in the UI of a designer host at design time.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma folha de editor do momento da conceção para as propriedades de um <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""> </xref> expressão na IU de um anfitrião do estruturador no momento da concepção.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditor> class together with the RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet class to select the individual properties of a `RouteValue` expression, and to combine the selected expression property values into a `RouteValue` expression.
trans-unit.target: O estruturador visual utiliza o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditor>classe juntamente com a classe de RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet para selecionar propriedades individuais de um `RouteValue` expressão e combinar os valores de propriedade da expressão selecionada para uma `RouteValue` expressão.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method returns a RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet object.

In the expressions dialog box, when you select a control property and bind it to a `RouteValue` expression, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Na caixa de diálogo expressões, quando seleciona uma propriedade de controlo e vinculá-lo para um `RouteValue` expressão, as chamadas de designer visual de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the returned RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet object to prompt for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValue%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O estruturador visual utiliza o objeto devolvido do RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet para solicitar o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValue%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: Once the property is selected, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A> method to create a `RouteValue` expression string.
trans-unit.target: Assim que a propriedade está selecionada, o estruturador visual chama o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>método para criar um `RouteValue` cadeia da expressão.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValue%2A> property must be specified in order to create a `RouteValue` expression string.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValue%2A>propriedade tem de ser especificada para criar um `RouteValue` cadeia da expressão.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: The initial <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValue%2A> property value is set using the input `expression` string.
trans-unit.target: Iniciais <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValue%2A>valor da propriedade está definido com a entrada `expression` cadeia.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteValueExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A> property is set using the input `serviceProvider` implementation.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>propriedade está definida com a entrada `serviceProvider` implementação.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""></xref> expression, used to initialize the expression editor sheet.
trans-unit.target: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""> </xref> expressão utilizada para inicializar a folha de editor de expressão.

trans-unit.source: A service provider implementation supplied by the designer host, used to obtain additional design-time services
trans-unit.target: Uma implementação do fornecedor de serviço fornecida pelo anfitrião de estruturador utilizado para obter os serviços de tempo de design adicionais

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""></xref> expression that is formed by the expression editor sheet property values.
trans-unit.target: Devolve um <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""> </xref> expressão que tem o formato de valores de propriedade da folha de editor de expressão.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""></xref> expression string for the current settings in the sheet.
trans-unit.target: O <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""> </xref> cadeia da expressão para as definições na folha atuais.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""></xref> expression string is valid.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""> </xref> cadeia da expressão é válida.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""></xref> expression string is valid; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se o <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""> </xref> cadeia da expressão é válido; caso contrário <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the URL parameter to be evaluated by the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""></xref> expression.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o nome do parâmetro a ser avaliado por URL de <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""> </xref> expressão.

trans-unit.source: The name of the URL parameter to be evaluated by the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""></xref> expression.
trans-unit.target: O nome do parâmetro a ser avaliado por URL de <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteValue" name="RouteValue" href=""> </xref> expressão.
